dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Decorative borders. Inset plan of the environs of Lisbon. View of the city is placed below the plan. Sheet is no. 45 of 'Meyers' Handatlas'.
dct_publisher_sm: Hildburghausen [Germany] : Aus der Geographischen Graviranstalt des Bibliographischen Instituts, 1844.
